org.cef.handler

Class CefCookieAccessFilterAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cef.handler.CefCookieAccessFilterAdapter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CefCookieAccessFilter 

    public abstract class CefCookieAccessFilterAdapter
extends java.lang.Object
implements CefCookieAccessFilter
    An abstract adapter class for cookie access filter events. The methods in this class are empty. This class exists as convenience for creating handler objects.(cookie访问筛选器事件的抽象适配器类。此类中的方法为空。此类的存在是为了方便创建处理程序对象。)

      • canSaveCookie

        public boolean canSaveCookie(CefBrowser browser,
                             CefFrame frame,
                             CefRequest request,
                             CefResponse response,
                             CefCookie cookie)
        Description copied from interface: CefCookieAccessFilter
        Called on the IO thread after a resource response is received. The |browser| and |frame| values represent the source of the request, and may be null for requests originating from service workers or CefURLRequest.(在收到资源响应后在IO线程上调用。|browser|和|frame|值表示请求的源，对于来自服务工作者或CefURLRequest的请求，它们可能为null。)
        Specified by:
        canSaveCookie in interface CefCookieAccessFilter
        Parameters:
        browser - The corresponding browser.(browser-相应的浏览器。)
        frame - The frame generating the event. Instance only valid within the scope of this method.(frame-生成事件的frame。实例仅在此方法的范围内有效。)
        request - The request itself. Cannot be modified in this callback. Instance only valid within the scope of this method.(request-请求本身。无法在此回调中修改。实例仅在此方法的范围内有效。)
        response - The request response. Cannot be modified in this callback. Instance only valid within the scope of this method.(response-请求响应。无法在此回调中修改。实例仅在此方法的范围内有效。)
        cookie - The cookie that will be sent with the request. Cannot be modified in this callback. Instance only valid within the scope of this method.(cookie-将与请求一起发送的cookie。无法在此回调中修改。实例仅在此方法的范围内有效。)
        Returns:
        True if the cookie can be saved or false otherwise.(如果可以保存cookie，则为True，否则为false。)
